<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Ad Review Request</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>New Advertisement Submitted</h2>
  <p>Hello Super Admin,</p>
  <p>An advertisement has been submitted for your review.</p>

  <h3>Advertisement Details:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= adTitle %></li>
    <li><strong>Submitted By (User ID):</strong> <%= requesterId %></li>
    <li><strong>Submitted Date:</strong> <%= submittedDate %></li>
    <li><strong>Advertisement ID:</strong> <%= adId %></li>
  </ul>

  <p>Please log in to the admin panel to review the ad.</p>

  <p>Regards,<br>Ad Management System</p>
</body>
</html>
